description: Demolition of Capital House, and erection of a 21 and 31 storey building (1 basement Level plus ground and 30 upper storeys) to a maximum height 108.788m to provide 119 residential units (C3), retail/cafe units (flexible Class A1, A3 Use) at ground floor level, 199 cycle parking spaces, 2 disabled car parking spaces, associated refuse and recycling, and an area of public open space.
